thread.title: Wayne Frith
thread.title_full: Otticanet recensione scritta da Wayne Frith

author: Wayne Frith
title: Wayne Frith
text: I ordered some oakley frames. I was sent an email saying the colour and size I wanted were out of stock and given other options. I chose some different frames and ordered them on Wednesday night and where delivered at 8.30 am Friday morning. I was very pleased with the commutation from otticanet and the delivery company they chose.
